[Student "S"]
{NORTH bids 3\S to show a strong hand with a singleton \S. 

After SOUTH shows her first-round \C control NORTH decides he will bid slam if SOUTH has three Aces.

When Blackwood reveals just two Aces in SOUTH, NORTH stops at 5\H.}

