[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/jacoby_2nt"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST bids 4\C after WEST's Jacoby 2NT. The reason for this bid is just to describe 
her hand as having a side 5-card \C suit. EAST knows the eventual contract will 
be some level of \Hs.

WEST doesn't have a strong hand, but he would show \D control at 
this time if he had the Ace. He isn't strong enough to go past game to show the \SA, so he 
just bids 4\H.}

[Event ""]
